properties.areaDesc: Melville Foothills; Southern Wheatland; Northern Sweet Grass
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 5 at 3:21PM MST until January 6 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Billings MT
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph expected.

* WHERE...Northern Sweet Grass, Melville Foothills and Southern
Wheatland.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 8 PM MST Monday. Strongest
winds late tonight through midday Monday.

* IMPACTS...Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile
vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use caution if you must drive and be prepared for sudden strong
crosswinds.

Additional graphics for this hazard can be found at
http://www.weather.gov/billings

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 8 PM MST MONDAY
